63693,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:05:25.000Z","msg":"以前學過好似叫滯脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"以前學過好似叫胃脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a48830cab68334086eba8634e6423f40b8d140b","tid":1963693,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fd90bdebe44c09f497591da542fbf51a50933a3","tid":1963693,"uid":35408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9255bbcebdf674d7da20e99748498e3c476aeb45","tid":1963693,"uid":6058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:05:25.000Z","msg":"以前學過好似叫滯脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:07:18.000Z","msg":"以前學過好似叫胃脹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"停滯性通貨膨脹（英語：stagflation），簡稱滯漲或停滯性通漲，在經濟學、特別是宏觀經濟學中，特指經濟停滯（stagnation），失業及通貨膨脹（inflation，此處指&quot;物價持續上漲&quot;）同時持續增長的經濟現象。滯漲（stagflation）作為混成詞起源於英國政治人物麥克勞德1965年在國會的演說中。<br />\n<br />\n這個概念值得注意的原因，部分基於在戰後的宏觀經濟學理論上，人們認為通貨膨漲與經濟衰退不能並存，亦因為人們廣泛認為滯漲與財政赤字一樣，一旦開始就難於根治。<br />\n<br />\n在政治場上滯脹以通貨膨漲痛苦指數（Misery index）來量度（簡單以失業率及通漲率相加），用以影響美國1976年及1980年的總統選舉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n搵返"},{"pid":"d69d50115b3770c3804d7f9fcda9cb54996486d3","tid":1963693,"uid":200780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5f03fa1a1c22be5f298f96b49480748146558346","tid":1963693,"uid":266503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T11:48:44.000Z","msg":"外國印錢係劫富濟貧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-08T16:08:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你肯定唔富者越富，貧者越貧"}]}